data.description: Charming 3 bed 2 bath home on one level. Bonus Room is upstairs above the garage. Plenty of room in the fenced backyard. Well placed neighborhood just around the corner from restaurants, grocery, shopping, parks, and more, yet still maintains a quiet vibe. Less than 30 minutes from Downtown Nashville, only 20 minutes to the airport, and 15 minutes to Percy Priest Lake or 10 minutes to Old Hickory Lake!
